comments: Both Gobert (MIN) and Theis (LAC) engage and disengage in marginal contact off ball.
Theis (LAC) establishes himself in McDaniels' (MIN) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Theis (LAC) establishes himself in McDaniels' (MIN) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Conley (MIN) legally contests Harden's (LAC) jump shot attempt.
Gobert (MIN) establishes himself in George's (LAC) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
George (LAC) legally contests Edwards' (MIN) jump shot attempt.
Conley (MIN) legally contests Leonard's (LAC) jump shot attempt.
Harden (LAC) makes marginal contact with Towns's (MIN) body while defending the drive to the basket and shot attempt.
McDaniels (MIN) briefly places his hand on Leonard's (LAC) side during the inbound.
Towns (MIN) initiates foot to foot contact with Harden (LAC) and affects his SQBR at the start of his drive.
Conley (MIN) commits a take foul on Leonard (LAC).
Gobert (MIN) briefly extends his arms into Coffey (LAC) but quickly retracts them while setting the screen.
